---
title: Roasted Portobello Sandwich with Balsamic Glazed Onions and Sweet Potatoes
description: You won't miss the beef in these hearty veggie-friendly portobello mushroom burgers topped with balsamic glazed onions. Don't forget to wipe up the extra pesto aioli with your sweet potatoes!
